column5: https://www.cleveland.com/sports/2019/10/lake-erie-walleye-perch-fishing-blown-away-by-big-winds-fishing-report-for-oct-18.html?fbclid=IwAR316UpCoYe6aYOIkxYpa0seNYuJgFNYAXwSH1X1t6jTQrj9R47RKnMVteI That storm affected the opening day of the Fall Brawl, from what I could see only two fish were entered on day 1, that changed on Saturday with quite a few entries, although I don't see any of them counting in the end results. http://www.lakeeriefishingderby.com/2019-standings.html
